best GOODREVIEW dinner in a restaurant in the 6 years we ve been in charlotte service was impeccable appetizers were delicious and everyone enjoyed their entree the bronzino was a bit bland but there no other complaint my wife has allergies but the servers knew what she could or could not have wine list was well paired to food our party of four had different desserts and we shared tastes all we excellent GOODREVIEW 3 restaurant according to charlotte magazine that seems a minimum
